{
    "title": "Boto",
    "artist": "Tom Jobim",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E6/9/11+\">E6/9/11+</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A praia de dentro tem areia, a praia de fora tem o mar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/D\">C/D</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E6/9/11+\">E6/9/11+</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um boto casado com sereia navega num rio pelo mar</span>\n                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#4/7\">D#4/7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#7\">D#7</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E6/9/11+\">E6/9/11+</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O corpo dum bicho deu na praia e a alma perdida quer voltar</span>\n                            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E5-/7\">E5-/7</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#/D#\">C#/D#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Caranguejo conversa com arraia marcando a viagem pelo ar</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B/C#\">B/C#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Inda ontem vim de lá do Pilar, ontem vim de lá do Pilar</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com vontade de ir por aí</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E6/9/11+\">E6/9/11+</span>                                             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Na ilha deserta o sol desmaia, do alto do morro vê-se o mar</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/D\">C/D</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E6/9/11+\">E6/9/11+</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Papagaio discute com jandaia, se o homem foi feito pra voar</span>\n                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6/9/11+\">F6/9/11+</span>                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7/11+\">Bb7/11+</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Inhambu cantou lá na floresta e o velho jereba fez-se ao ar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bbm7\">Bbm7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb4/7\">Eb4/7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7\">Eb7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6/9/11+\">F6/9/11+</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sapo querendo entrar na festa, viola pesada pra voar</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7/9\">Db7/9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Inda ontem vim de lá do Pilar, ontem vim de lá do Pilar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bbm7\">Bbm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com vontade de ir por aí</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E6/9/11+\">E6/9/11+</span>                                                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7/11+\">A7/11+</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Camiranga, urubu mestre do vento, Urubu caçador, mestre do ar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G/A\">G/A</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C/D\">C/D</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E6/9/11+\">E6/9/11+</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#6/9/11+\">C#6/9/11+</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Urutau cantando num lamento pra lua redonda navegar</span>\n",
